## Project Structure ğŸ“

```
SuperGemini/
â”œâ”€â”€ setup.py               # pypi setup file
â”œâ”€â”€ SuperGemini/           # Framework files  
â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ Core/              # Behavior documentation (COMMANDS.md, FLAGS.md, etc.)
